fslpy - front end to the FSL tools.

Dependencies:

 - PyOpenGL   3.1.0
 - numpy      1.8.1
 - scipy      0.14.0
 - matplotlib 1.3.1
 - nibabel    1.3.0
 - Pillow     2.5.3 (for screenshots of any type other than PNG)

 - wxPython   3.0.0.0

 - OSMesa 6.5.3 (for off-screen rendering)

 - OpenGL. Either
   - OpenGL 1.4, with the following extensions:
     - ARB_vertex_program
     - ARB_fragment_program
   - OpenGL 2.1

